title: 이달의소녀탐구 #409 (LOONA TV #409)
summary:
0:02 -- YeoJin starts off the episode by flaunting her dress. She feels ashamed as she has to run with HaSeul while holding her hand but she thinks the weather will be warm.
0:19 -- Their scene starts to get shot.
0:44 -- MomSeul is back at guiding YeoJin and the shooting finally ends.
0:50 -- YeoJin feels confused. HaSeul: "Did you have fun?"; YeoJin: "Yes I had fun!"
